flowchart LR
    subgraph release[Release Pipeline]
        Main[Push to Main] --> AppToken[GitHub App Token]
        AppToken --> RP[Release-Please]
        RP --> PR[Creates PR]
    end

    subgraph build[Build Pipeline]
        PR -->|pull_request event| DC[Detect Changes]
        DC --> Test[Test]
        Test --> Build[Build]
        Build --> Status[Build Status]
    end

